      "content": "everything is just so quiet now. i wake up and for a split second i forget, and then it hits me all over again. it feels like i'm just walking through a house that isn't mine anymore. what's even the point of doing any of this? the routine, the eating, the breathing... it all just feels so heavy and pointless without him.",
